ences and applied research, he can provide unbiased, clear, and timely explanations nationwide.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[button href=\"/contact/\"]Start to Solve Your Case[/button]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode --></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\" style=\"\" id=\"\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"><img src=\"http://discovery-engineering.local/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Mark-McFarland.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\" id=\"\"/></div></div></div></section></div>\n<!-- /wp:create-block/content-image -->\n\n<!-- wp:create-block/content-block {\"section_style\":\"padding-bottom:0px;\",\"section_class\":\"bg-light\",\"col_class\":\"col-lg-12 text-center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-create-block-content-block\"><section class=\"position-relative bg-light\" style=\"padding:50px 0;padding-bottom:0px;\" id=\"\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"col-lg-12 text-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\" data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Forensic Engineering &amp; Applied Research Expertise</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div></div></section></div>\n<!-- /wp:create-block/content-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:create-block/boxes-title-content {\"section_style\":\"padding-top:5px;\",\"section_class\":\"bg-light\",\"columns\":[{\"col_class\":\"col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch\",\"col_style\":\"margin: 20px 0;paddin\",\"col_id\":\"02\",\"img\":\"\",\"title\":\"Wireless and Telecommunications Engineering\",\"content\":\"Over 25 years of experience in research, design, analysis, \\u0026 measurement of cellular, GPS, 3G5G, LTE, public safety comm systems, satellite, Internet, wireless, RF, Wi-Fi, radar, networks, data communications, communications protocols and standards, instrumentation, and control systems.\",\"inner_col_style\":\"box-shadow:0px 0px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);padding:20px;\",\"inner_col_class\":\"bg-white\"},{\"col_c